---
// src/components/home/Hero.astro
---
<section class="py-12 md:py-20 mt-18 md:mt-28 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden relative container mx-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 md:gap-12 px:0 md:px-20">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left animate-slideInLeft p-4">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-blue-800 leading-tight mb-4" style="font-family: 'Montserrat';">
                Agencia de <span class="block text-purple-600">Marketing Digital</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6 max-w-lg md:max-w-none mx-auto md:mx-0">
                Si buscas una empresa de <strong>marketing digital</strong> que ayude a tu negocio a crecer, en Pixel Pro tenemos las estrategias perfectas para ti. Con experiencia en <strong>SEO</strong>, <strong>gestión de redes sociales</strong> y <strong>campañas de Google Ads</strong>, mejoramos tu visibilidad y atraemos más clientes. ¡Haz que tu marca se destaque en el mundo digital!
            </p>
            <!-- <ul class="text-gray-600 text-base md:text-lg mb-8 space-y-2 text-left inline-block md:block">
                <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-2"></i> Estrategias Personalizadas</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-2"></i> Resultados Medibles</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-2"></i> Visibilidad Total</li>
            </ul> -->
            <a href="/contacto" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
                Solicita tu Presupuesto
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center md:justify-end animate-slideInRight p-4">
            <img
                src="/assets/img/agencia-de-marketing-digital.webp"
                alt="Equipo de marketing digital trabajando y analizando datos"
                class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl max-w-full h-auto object-cover transform hover:scale-102 transition-transform duration-500"
                loading="eager"
            />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-200 opacity-20 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-0"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-48 h-48 bg-purple-200 opacity-20 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 z-0"></div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes fadeInDown {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes slideInLeft {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-50px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
    }
    @keyframes slideInRight {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(50px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
    }

    .animate-fadeInDown { animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease-out forwards; }
    .animate-fadeInUp { animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards; }
    .animate-slideInLeft { animation: slideInLeft 1s ease-out forwards; }
    .animate-slideInRight { animation: slideInRight 1s ease-out forwards; }
</style>